beer.beer_description: Diggin’ this Hazy IPA with oat and wheat lending a silky smooth soft base of which Sabro, Nelson Sauvin and Vic Secret shine through in all their tropical glory. Fluctuating flavours brought together like a bangin’ fruit salad by our house NEIPA yeast. Expect a haze bomb that is silky smooth and gently bitter, with rad hits of pineapple, passionfruit, peach and mango vibin’ to unique notes of coconut and papaya.
